         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">1/4/70 ¶  ¶ Herewith, dear Mr ¶ .  ¶ Ware, I beg to send the application for additional fund to pay wages for March, also Salaries. I have no copy of the estimate for 1870; perhaps you will oblige me ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.04.01</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Ware</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">V70/3531, unit 464, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Trans. by Angela. To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See also M to J. MacPherson, 2 April 1870.</p>
               </note>1/4/70</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Herewith, dear Mr<seg style="font-size: 10pt; ">. </seg>Ware, I beg to send the application for additional fund to pay wages for March, also Salaries. I have no copy of the estimate for 1870; perhaps you will oblige me by putting into the application form the number of the division and subdivision.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Your very regardful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Approval for M's application was minuted to this letter.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
